  <brief_title>Dyspnea Threshold During 6 Minutes Walk Test</brief_title>
  <acronym>SD6</acronym>
  <official_title>Self-perception of Dyspnea Threshold During the 6-minute Walk Test (DT6): A New Tool for Individualized Exercise Training With Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease Patients (COPD)</official_title>
