  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      In view of the multiple limitations and restrictions relative to CPET (technical, time,
      physical…), determination of individualized training threshold from this evaluation is today
      not possible for a lot of patients.

      The aim of this study was to propose a new clinical tool from 6MWT for individualized
      exercise training: the dyspnea threshold (DT6).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
