      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  COPD

          -  with or without rest and/or ambulation oxygen therapy

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  exacerbation in the previous four weeks

          -  with a restrictive or mixed respiratory syndrome, angina , recent heart attack (&lt; 1
             month) or coronary progressive pathology

          -  under beta-blockers

          -  cognitive or motor problems which limit significantly comprehension or achievement of
             evaluations
